net.sf.marineapi.nmea.parser
Class PositionParser

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.marineapi.nmea.parser.SentenceParser
      net.sf.marineapi.nmea.parser.PositionParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
Sentence
public abstract class PositionParser
extends SentenceParser

Abstract base class for sentence parsers that provide geographic position or waypoint data, and thus need to parse lat/lon values. However, notice that PositionParser does not implement PositionSentence interface because the extending parser may not provide current location.

$Revision: 23 $
